[12/03, 10:36 am] Meta AI: Here is a simple HTML and CSS program:

Simple Web Page with CSS Styling
*HTML Code (index.html)*
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My Web Page</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to My Web Page</h1>
  <p>This is my first web page with CSS styling.</p>
  <button>Click Me!</button>
</body>
</html>
```

*CSS Code (style.css)*
```
body {
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

h1 {
  color: #00698f;
  text-align: center;
}

p {
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

button {
  background-color: #4CAF50;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
  background-color: #3e8e41
}
